---
title: Classic Cheeseburger and Seasoned Fries with Burger Sauce and Balsamic Rocket Salad
description: This Classic Cheeseburger and Seasoned Fries is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W38_UK_F13299-3_Main_low-2a8fa319.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/64b7b651a7c1f8a1e13bb53e.pdf
